00:41:34.800 --> 00:41:38.166
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:41:48.959 --> 00:41:51.917
But the truth has two sides:

00:41:54.917 --> 00:41:59.417
the illusion that we see can look like truth,

00:42:04.041 --> 00:42:08.250
and the essence of the illusion also may appear to be truth.

00:42:14.000 --> 00:42:18.333
But the other side is absolute

00:42:23.583 --> 00:42:25.625
and has to be felt,

00:42:27.542 --> 00:42:29.041
has to be experienced

00:42:31.875 --> 00:42:34.041
on your central nervous system.

00:42:38.125 --> 00:42:41.542
It's not a mental projection that we can think of,

00:42:46.125 --> 00:42:48.000
nor emotional imagination,

00:42:51.625 --> 00:42:55.792
but truth is what it is, it cannot be changed.

00:43:00.917 --> 00:43:02.999
It cannot compromise.

00:43:06.250 --> 00:43:09.917
We have to humble down ourselves to know the truth.

00:43:15.166 --> 00:43:19.250
Now we have discovered so many things in the science,

00:43:23.875 --> 00:43:28.709
by humility that we have not known so far.

00:43:32.999 --> 00:43:38.291
But whatever is known outside, like the tree must have roots,

00:43:44.875 --> 00:43:47.834
and these roots are not known

00:43:48.125 --> 00:43:52.458
if you are just looking at the tree.

00:43:57.125 --> 00:43:59.709
And when somebody talks about the roots,

00:43:59.999 --> 00:44:00.999
we get shaken up

00:44:01.291 --> 00:44:04.583
because we have had no knowledge of it before.

00:44:11.542 --> 00:44:14.792
Thus we are conditioned to only see the tree,

00:44:15.083 --> 00:44:19.125
and we cannot make our mind understand

00:44:19.458 --> 00:44:22.291
that there must be some roots to it.

00:44:30.250 --> 00:44:31.291
So we can say

00:44:31.542 --> 00:44:34.291
that people have advanced in science quite a lot,

00:44:34.583 --> 00:44:38.250
and have progressed and have become developed countries.

00:44:38.583 --> 00:44:41.709
But they do not know, if they do not seek their roots

00:44:41.999 --> 00:44:45.041
they will be completely destroyed.

00:44:56.834 --> 00:44:58.667
Now when I'm before you,

00:44:58.999 --> 00:45:04.500
one should not in any way feel that I'm here to offend you,

00:45:12.333 --> 00:45:16.500
but I've come here to tell you about the roots,

00:45:17.041 --> 00:45:19.750
the great properties you have within yourself.

00:45:27.834 --> 00:45:32.125
We know about so many energies around us like electricity,

00:45:32.417 --> 00:45:36.500
gravity, in the scientific field of knowledge.

00:45:43.125 --> 00:45:45.834
But there are subtler energies within us

00:45:46.083 --> 00:45:47.750
which we should try to understand

00:45:48.041 --> 00:45:50.375
with the same humility of a scientist,

00:45:50.709 --> 00:45:52.709
and the open-mindedness.

00:46:03.000 --> 00:46:06.500
Now what problems are facing us here in the West,

00:46:06.834 --> 00:46:08.083
we should try to understand.

00:46:08.375 --> 00:46:11.750
As somebody in America asked Me, "What's wrong with the West?"

00:46:21.500 --> 00:46:26.041
We have to see what has happened to us in our evolution.

00:46:31.750 --> 00:46:34.999
When we evolved through the industrial development,

00:46:35.291 --> 00:46:38.709
we developed certain temperaments and certain value system.

00:46:48.834 --> 00:46:51.250
Industrialization was a good idea,

00:46:51.583 --> 00:46:53.917
but there is no discretion where to stop it.

00:46:59.917 --> 00:47:03.375
And that's how when we go to very industrialized countries

00:47:03.667 --> 00:47:06.834
we think we are just eating chemicals and not food.

00:47:15.041 --> 00:47:17.583
Now the balance has to be maintained,

00:47:20.959 --> 00:47:22.375
but how?

00:47:23.250 --> 00:47:25.375
By knowing about the roots.

00:47:28.750 --> 00:47:33.041
Now the first problem I feel about the Western mind

00:47:33.333 --> 00:47:36.917
is that it is a mental being;

00:47:43.458 --> 00:47:48.750
it has developed this mental capacity beyond balance.

00:47:52.750 --> 00:47:56.709
Like in the industries we have to have new things

00:47:56.999 --> 00:47:57.959
made all the time;

00:47:58.291 --> 00:48:00.875
every time we have to sell some goods

00:48:01.208 --> 00:48:02.542
we must have new fashions,

00:48:02.875 --> 00:48:05.333
otherwise the machines will be starving.

00:48:24.500 --> 00:48:29.083
In the same way our brain starts producing new things,

00:48:35.000 --> 00:48:38.583
that's how these things are man-made.

00:48:43.999 --> 00:48:47.291
With mental projection we start thinking

00:48:47.625 --> 00:48:49.291
of all the time new things

00:48:49.625 --> 00:48:52.250
and we appreciate whatever comes new to us.

00:49:00.250 --> 00:49:02.625
We have to take to new things,

00:49:02.917 --> 00:49:06.709
but not to something that is absolutely devoid

00:49:07.041 --> 00:49:09.375
of any traditional value.

00:49:18.500 --> 00:49:20.959
Like the other day I said that

00:49:21.250 --> 00:49:22.625
"What's so special about Freud,

00:49:22.959 --> 00:49:26.000
why did you accept him and why not Jung?"

00:49:34.999 --> 00:49:40.250
The reason was given that he gave us very new ideas.

00:49:44.917 --> 00:49:47.709
Anything new is not always good;

00:49:48.000 --> 00:49:50.667
for example plastic was new once upon a time,

00:49:51.000 --> 00:49:54.000
you know what are the results of plastic development.

00:50:01.333 --> 00:50:05.250
If that is true about matter, what about the spirit?

00:50:09.999 --> 00:50:12.333
So when we seek also the truth,

00:50:12.625 --> 00:50:16.375
we try to get to a new method all the time.

00:50:23.375 --> 00:50:25.291
And I think the evil

00:50:25.625 --> 00:50:30.333
that came in forms of wrong type of gurus

00:50:30.750 --> 00:50:34.709
are the product of this kind of demand.

00:50:51.500 --> 00:50:55.667
Only seventy to hundred years back, I should say, in India,

00:50:55.959 --> 00:50:59.583
suddenly a new wave of some new ideas

00:50:59.917 --> 00:51:02.917
about the knowledge of the roots started.

00:51:11.125 --> 00:51:14.709
Some things that they talk of are not written in the Vedas

00:51:15.041 --> 00:51:21.375
nor in the Puranas, nor in any books of oriental knowledge;

00:51:31.417 --> 00:51:35.875
nor in any books that are written after Christ

00:51:36.125 --> 00:51:41.125
like the Bible, or Koran after Mohammed Sahib,

00:51:41.458 --> 00:51:45.125
and also the writings of Zoroaster.

00:51:55.083 --> 00:51:57.458
It has no relationship whatsoever

00:51:57.750 --> 00:52:00.959
to the ancient findings about the roots.

00:52:09.291 --> 00:52:14.125
So we had a problem about the religion in the same manner.

00:52:20.750 --> 00:52:23.709
For example, let us take Christianity:

00:52:26.458 --> 00:52:30.625
Christ came on this Earth, as you will know later on,

00:52:30.959 --> 00:52:34.834
to create a special awareness within us of the spirit.

00:52:44.208 --> 00:52:47.542
He resides inside within us

00:52:50.041 --> 00:52:54.417
in a special center, what we call the Agnya Chakra,

00:52:59.208 --> 00:53:04.291
and described in the Indian scriptures as Mahavishnu.

00:53:09.250 --> 00:53:10.917
And in the purest form

00:53:11.208 --> 00:53:14.959
He exists as the Omkara, as the Logos.

00:53:20.750 --> 00:53:23.291
So much is described about Him in the West,

00:53:23.583 --> 00:53:27.250
in the Western knowledge

00:53:27.667 --> 00:53:28.959
in the mental way,

00:53:29.208 --> 00:53:31.583
but actually it is very much discovered

00:53:31.959 --> 00:53:34.458
in the Indian philosophy.

00:53:50.667 --> 00:53:55.250
You cannot understand Christ by mental projection,

00:53:59.750 --> 00:54:01.834
because He is beyond mind.

00:54:04.667 --> 00:54:08.000
He has Himself said, "You are to be born again."

00:54:12.792 --> 00:54:17.458
When Nicodemus said, "What do you mean â€˜to be born again'?

