00:54:33.000 --> 00:54:36.542
and you are to be born of the Holy Ghost."

00:54:43.750 --> 00:54:45.750
And what is the Holy Ghost?

00:54:47.709 --> 00:54:50.125
The bishop of Canterbury was asked this question,

00:54:50.458 --> 00:54:53.917
I saw it on the television, and he says, "I am agnostic."

00:55:04.083 --> 00:55:06.333
