which catches when you feel guilty.

01:47:59.959 --> 01:48:03.250
Look at it as if you are looking at something jocular.

01:48:03.583 --> 01:48:06.083
What is there to feel guilty?

01:48:14.583 --> 01:48:16.083
Another mental projection;

01:48:18.667 --> 01:48:20.667
it's an illusion.

01:48:21.208 --> 01:48:23.834
All right. Now, then you have to place your hand

01:48:24.041 --> 01:48:28.041
on top of your forehead across like this,

01:48:32.250 --> 01:48:34.709
and then on the back.

01:48:37.625 --> 01:48:40.250
Then you have to stretch your palm

01:48:40.709 --> 01:48:45.250
and put this part on the fontanel bone area.

01:48:51.667 --> 01:48:55.999
Press it hard, and you have to move it seven times clockwise

01:48:56.291 --> 01:48:58.667
when I tell you.

01:49:08.500 --> 01:49:11.417
Now, do not try to stop your thoughts or anything,

01:49:11.750 --> 01:49:14.208
it will all work out spontaneously.

01:49:20.458 --> 01:49:22.166
If there are too much thoughts,

01:49:22.500 --> 01:49:25.875
then you can put your attention here on the fontanel bone.

01:49:32.250 --> 01:49:34.375
So let us start now.

01:49:37.208 --> 01:49:39.291
All of you must do it.

01:49:39.583 --> 01:49:42.041
If those who do not want to do it should go out,

01:49:42.542 --> 01:49:45.959
don't trouble others, because others become self-conscious.

01:50:02.166 --> 01:50:04.458
It is not civil.

01:50:07.417 --> 01:50:12.333
Now, everyone has to close the eyes.

01:50:16.417 --> 01:50:18.917
Take out your spectacles

01:50:23.917 --> 01:50:25.417
because you don't have to see anything,

01:50:25.709 --> 01:50:28.250
you have to keep your eyes shut.

01:50:47.375 --> 01:50:49.750
Now.

01:50:52.625 --> 01:50:55.750
Now, put your left hand towards Me just like this,

01:51:01.959 --> 01:51:04.625
and have faith in yourself.

01:51:09.250 --> 01:51:12.000
Now, forgive yourself and close your eyes,

01:51:12.375 --> 01:51:14.542
keep your eyes shut.

01:51:20.959 --> 01:51:23.917
Close your eyes, put your right hand on your heart

01:51:24.166 --> 01:51:26.625
and left hand towards Me.

01:51:33.667 --> 01:51:36.000
On your heart.

01:51:36.458 --> 01:51:39.709
Left hand towards Me and right hand to be used

01:51:40.041 --> 01:51:43.709
for the action. Tell them.

01:51:51.333 --> 01:51:54.166
Now, please put your right hand on the heart,

01:51:54.500 --> 01:51:56.500
right hand on the heart.

01:52:02.542 --> 01:52:07.500
So the left hand has to be kept on your lap, upward.

01:52:17.667 --> 01:52:20.333
Be comfortable,

01:52:21.542 --> 01:52:24.041
you have to be comfortable.

01:52:31.375 --> 01:52:36.333
Now, you have to ask Me

01:52:37.250 --> 01:52:39.999
a very fundamental question.

01:52:44.417 --> 01:52:46.999
In the heart resides the spirit,

01:52:47.291 --> 01:52:50.834
so please ask Me a question three times,

01:52:51.125 --> 01:52:53.333
"Mother, am I the spirit?"

01:52:53.625 --> 01:52:56.375
If you can call Me "Shri Mataji" it's all right, or "Mother"

01:52:56.709 --> 01:52:58.709
- whichever suits you.

01:53:31.125 --> 01:53:34.208
You must really have faith in yourself.

01:53:57.709 --> 01:54:01.875
Now, take down this right hand on your stomach,

01:54:02.125 --> 01:54:05.291
on the upper part on the left-hand side,

01:54:14.125 --> 01:54:16.000
and press it.

01:54:20.166 --> 01:54:24.250
This is the center of the mastery,

01:54:29.375 --> 01:54:33.417
which is created by prophets who came on this earth.

01:54:38.667 --> 01:54:43.000
So here, you have to ask Me another question.

01:54:43.375 --> 01:54:48.709
If you are your spirit, then you have to be your own guide.

01:54:49.083 --> 01:54:52.542
So you have to say, "Mother, am I my own guide?

01:55:12.834 --> 01:55:14.792
Am I the prophet?

01:55:19.542 --> 01:55:22.208
Am I my own guru,

01:55:27.417 --> 01:55:29.999
am I my own master?"

01:56:01.291 --> 01:56:04.999
Three times.

01:56:10.208 --> 01:56:13.458
Now, please take down your hand

01:56:13.792 --> 01:56:16.583
in the lower part of the abdomen and press it.

01:56:26.375 --> 01:56:28.999
This is the center

01:56:33.458 --> 01:56:38.041
of the knowledge about the Divine.

01:56:44.959 --> 01:56:47.208
This knowledge is not mental,

01:56:47.542 --> 01:56:49.250
but the technique

01:56:49.625 --> 01:56:54.166
that builds into your central nervous system.

01:57:04.291 --> 01:57:09.000
So here you have to say something,

01:57:09.625 --> 01:57:12.500
because I cannot force you

01:57:13.166 --> 01:57:19.458
to accept the procedure of kundalini awakening.

01:57:32.999 --> 01:57:37.166
Now, you have to yourself ask

01:57:37.709 --> 01:57:41.041
that you want to know about the true knowledge,

01:57:41.375 --> 01:57:43.125
about the pure knowledge.

01:57:43.500 --> 01:57:44.834
So please say six times,

01:57:45.166 --> 01:57:48.000
"Mother, may I have the true knowledge?

01:57:48.291 --> 01:57:50.625
May I have the pure knowledge?"

01:57:50.959 --> 01:57:54.542
With this saying the kundalini will start moving.

01:58:24.625 --> 01:58:27.458
Six times, please ask the question,

01:58:27.750 --> 01:58:31.375
"Mother, please may I have the true knowledge,

01:58:31.875 --> 01:58:34.291
the pure knowledge?"

01:59:10.291 --> 01:59:14.458
Now we have to make way for the kundalini, which is awakened.

01:59:14.792 --> 01:59:16.250
Please keep your eyes shut.

01:59:22.834 --> 01:59:24.000
Raise your right hand

01:59:24.333 --> 01:59:27.417
and put it in the upper part of the abdomen.

01:59:37.250 --> 01:59:41.041
Now, please keep your eyes shut, don't open in between,

01:59:41.375 --> 01:59:43.500
because attention has to go inside.

01:59:50.750 --> 01:59:55.834
At this point, as I told you, is the center of your mastery.

02:00:07.166 --> 02:00:13.583
Now here you have to say with full faith in yourself,

02:00:13.999 --> 02:00:15.917
asserting,

02:00:18.291 --> 02:00:21.792
"Mother, I am my own master.

02:00:30.625 --> 02:00:34.667
I am my own guide, I am my own prophet."

02:00:43.125 --> 02:00:45.500
Please say it ten times.

02:01:17.917 --> 02:01:20.166
Please do not feel guilty when you say that,

02:01:20.458 --> 02:01:21.959
please do not feel guilty.

02:01:30.500 --> 02:01:33.291
You are the prophet.

02:01:35.834 --> 02:01:40.333
William Blake has said that "Men of God," meaning seekers,

02:01:40.999 --> 02:01:42.041
"will become prophets,

02:01:42.333 --> 02:01:44.917
and they'll have powers to make others prophets."

02:01:56.834 --> 02:01:58.959
You are the men of God,

02:02:02.999 --> 02:02:05.500
and you will become prophets.

02:02:06.792 --> 02:02:09.500
Ah - now, better.

02:02:12.083 --> 02:02:14.834
William Blake helped!

02:02:34.000 --> 02:02:37.875
Now, please raise your hand to your heart.

02:02:42.792 --> 02:02:45.375
You should not say things speedily,

02:02:45.709 --> 02:02:48.542
but with understanding and with depth.

02:03:01.333 --> 02:03:05.375
Now at this point you have to again assert

02:03:05.709 --> 02:03:07.917
with full confidence in yourself and say,

02:03:08.250 --> 02:03:12.500
"Mother, I am the spirit." Say it twelve times, please

02:04:02.000 --> 02:04:06.999
... Now, now better. Working out.

02:04:50.000 --> 02:04:55.917
Now, raise your hand onto the corner

02:04:56.625 --> 02:05:01.166
between your neck and the shoulder.

02:05:09.417 --> 02:05:15.041
Take it quite back so that you can press on the bone.

02:05:26.458 --> 02:05:29.709
Here you have to say,

02:05:32.750 --> 02:05:34.792
with full faith in yourself,

02:05:35.083 --> 02:05:38.917
"Mother, I'm not guilty at all."

02:05:48.834 --> 02:05:54.500
You have to know that apart from God

02:05:54.917 --> 02:05:59.667
who is the ocean of love and compassion,

02:06:00.041 --> 02:06:05.667
above all He is the ocean of forgiveness.

02:06:16.917 --> 02:06:20.000
Whatever your guilt may be,

02:06:20.542 --> 02:06:24.667
compared to the power of the Divine to forgive,

02:06:24.959 --> 02:06:27.500
you cannot have any guilt.

02:06:38.417 --> 02:06:43.542
So please say sixteen times, "Mother, I'm not guilty at all."

02:07:24.083 --> 02:07:27.834
Even some people feel that they cannot believe

02:07:28.125 --> 02:07:29.792
that they are not guilty,

02:07:30.125 --> 02:07:33.542
so to punish themselves they can say it 108 times!

02:07:47.458 --> 02:07:49.750
That's better.

02:07:50.083 --> 02:07:53.625
Nobody wants to have the punishment, is a good idea.

02:08:02.667 --> 02:08:05.083
Better?

02:08:08.583 --> 02:08:13.583
Now, raise your hand to your forehead, please

02:08:19.709 --> 02:08:24.208
and - with the palm towards your forehead,

02:08:24.542 --> 02:08:27.250
and press it on both the sides.

02:08:31.333 --> 02:08:34.542
Put it across, across.

02:08:41.750 --> 02:08:44.500
I mean, place it horizontally.

02:08:48.583 --> 02:08:51.417
And now press it hard.

02:08:58.000 --> 02:09:00.750
Here you have to say, not how many times

02:09:01.000 --> 02:09:02.667
but from your heart,

02:09:02.959 --> 02:09:05.667
"Mother, I forgive everyone."

02:09:15.166 --> 02:09:17.625
Some people think that it's difficult,

02:09:17.959 --> 02:09:19.667
but it is a myth when you believe

02:09:20.000 --> 02:09:22.792
that you forgive or you don't forgive.

02:09:33.208 --> 02:09:37.542
But if you forgive everyone,

02:09:38.041 --> 02:09:42.291
then you do not play into the hands of wrong people

02:09:42.625 --> 02:09:45.041
- in a mythical way, of course.

02:09:58.917 --> 02:10:04.583
Now, raise your hand and take it backwards

02:10:05.500 --> 02:10:09.709
to your back side of your head, and hold it tight.

02:10:17.999 --> 02:10:21.542
Press your hand little backward and hold it tight.

02:10:25.959 --> 02:10:29.417
Now here you have to say,

02:10:30.500 --> 02:10:33.583
for your own satisfaction maybe,

02:10:34.834 --> 02:10:37.291
that "Oh Divine, please forgive me

02:10:37.625 --> 02:10:41.999
if I have done anything wrong against You."

02:11:14.333 --> 02:11:15.999
Now stretch your hand,

02:11:16.208 --> 02:11:18.625
and put your palm on top of your head

02:11:18.999 --> 02:11:23.166
on the fontanel bone area and press it hard, very hard,

02:11:23.417 --> 02:11:24.999
in a clockwise manner,

02:11:25.250 --> 02:11:30.333
saying one thing, that you want your realization;

02:11:30.625 --> 02:11:33.667
because I cannot cross your freedom here again.

02:11:33.999 --> 02:11:36.959
So please say, "Mother, I want my realization.

02:11:37.208 --> 02:11:40.417
Please give me my realization," seven times.

02:11:49.208 --> 02:11:52.417
Press it with the palm only, not with the fingers.

02:13:52.999 --> 02:13:56.667
Now take down your hand slowly,

02:14:01.959 --> 02:14:05.208
open your eyes slowly.

02:14:10.208 --> 02:14:14.125
Place your right hand towards Me,

02:14:17.625 --> 02:14:22.125
and with the left hand you place it on your top of your head.

02:14:26.291 --> 02:14:28.041
Don't think, don't think,

02:14:28.333 --> 02:14:31.166
see if there's a cool breeze coming out.

02:14:46.542 --> 02:14:48.834
Change your hand, please.

02:14:50.458 --> 02:14:52.834
Put your right hand

02:14:54.792 --> 02:14:58.583
and see for yourself if there's a cool breeze coming out.

02:15:06.709 --> 02:15:09.208
Don't be nervous;

02:15:10.166 --> 02:15:13.375
it is subtle, it is very subtle.

02:15:15.999 --> 02:15:18.750
Now, change over again.

02:15:30.750 --> 02:15:34.000
Now, put your hands up like this and push back your head,

02:15:34.375 --> 02:15:36.999
and ask a question.

02:15:41.417 --> 02:15:46.999
On the mike - come nearer to the mike.

02:15:47.583 --> 02:15:48.750
Now ask a question,

02:15:48.999 --> 02:15:51.750
"Mother, is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?

02:15:52.041 --> 02:15:53.750
Is this the Brahma Shakti?

02:15:54.041 --> 02:15:59.500
Is this the all-pervading God's love?"

02:16:17.125 --> 02:16:20.500
Now, bring down your hands, please.

02:16:22.583 --> 02:16:25.417
See for yourself.

02:16:26.709 --> 02:16:31.959
Don't think. Are you feeling it on your hand?

02:16:42.083 --> 02:16:45.291
Those who are feeling cool breeze on their hand

02:16:45.667 --> 02:16:48.166
- it's very subtle - or out of their head,

02:16:48.500 --> 02:16:51.458
please raise your both the hands.

02:17:07.417 --> 02:17:09.875
Most of you have felt it.

02:17:10.250 --> 02:17:13.000
But I will now tell you how to protect yourself,

02:17:13.291 --> 02:17:15.041
all of you should know how to protect;

02:17:15.458 --> 02:17:18.999
because some have not felt because they have a problem here,

02:17:19.375 --> 02:17:20.583
in the Vishuddhi Chakra.

02:17:20.875 --> 02:17:23.834
Or maybe they have not forgiven others.

02:17:41.834 --> 02:17:43.959
Try this. Put your right hand towards Me

02:17:44.208 --> 02:17:47.166
and your left hand like this, for balancing

02:17:54.000 --> 02:17:56.625
- to the sky.

02:18:01.417 --> 02:18:04.875
This is now we use the ether.

02:18:22.083 --> 02:18:25.041
If you are feeling the cool or something down below,

02:18:25.333 --> 02:18:27.917
put it back like that,

02:18:28.166 --> 02:18:30.959
if you are feeling down below.

02:18:38.792 --> 02:18:43.041
These people are very speedy and they are very right-sided,

02:18:43.417 --> 02:18:45.000
so this is the problem they have.

02:18:45.250 --> 02:18:47.792
Doesn't matter, it will work out.

02:18:55.583 --> 02:18:58.083
Think too much!

02:19:02.250 --> 02:19:04.709
Futuristic, they are futuristic.

02:19:10.959 --> 02:19:16.291
Facing your problems only, you solve them.

02:19:21.041 --> 02:19:23.125
Not mental projection

02:19:23.500 --> 02:19:25.709
but facing, just seeing them as they are.

02:19:31.500 --> 02:19:33.458
You are the spirit, you are not the problem;

02:19:33.834 --> 02:19:35.792
you are beyond all this.

02:19:40.125 --> 02:19:41.834
After realization the word "problem"

02:19:42.083 --> 02:19:44.999
goes out of your dictionary!

02:19:52.000 --> 02:19:54.500
Now, put the left hand like this

02:19:54.750 --> 02:19:57.625
and the right hand towards the Mother Earth ....

02:20:08.291 --> 02:20:11.792
Better, much better.

02:20:33.458 --> 02:20:36.000
Don't think.

02:20:37.041 --> 02:20:39.999
You can do it now.

