Now, I will tell you how to protect. It's very simple.

02:20:59.041 --> 02:21:03.583
You have to give protection to your auras.

02:21:03.917 --> 02:21:06.625
You can wear your glasses if you want to.

02:21:13.959 --> 02:21:15.125
That you must all do,

02:21:15.417 --> 02:21:18.208
whether you have felt the cool breeze or not.

02:21:23.458 --> 02:21:26.083
You give protection to your auras in this manner,

02:21:26.417 --> 02:21:27.875
that you put left hand like this

02:21:28.166 --> 02:21:30.125
and right hand around the auras,

02:21:30.458 --> 02:21:33.959
you take over your head and bring it down like that.

02:21:37.208 --> 02:21:39.458
Left hand towards Me.

02:21:49.792 --> 02:21:53.041
All right, let's do it seven times, for seven auras.

02:21:56.125 --> 02:21:59.375
One - don't think.

02:22:00.542 --> 02:22:03.375
Don't think!

02:22:05.041 --> 02:22:07.000
Three,

02:22:08.917 --> 02:22:11.583
four,

02:22:12.542 --> 02:22:15.041
five,

02:22:16.250 --> 02:22:18.291
six

02:22:18.792 --> 02:22:21.875
and seven.

02:22:22.291 --> 02:22:23.500
It's important.

02:22:23.792 --> 02:22:26.417
Now, how to raise your own kundalini,

02:22:26.709 --> 02:22:28.333
that's very simple again.

02:22:34.250 --> 02:22:37.375
Now put your left hand in front of your kundalini

02:22:37.709 --> 02:22:40.625
- you yourself can do it.

02:22:47.208 --> 02:22:50.750
And it should be moved from up, forward, down,

02:22:51.000 --> 02:22:53.667
like that clockwise, right hand.

02:22:53.959 --> 02:22:58.000
Left hand should be steady, left hand should be straight.

02:23:07.583 --> 02:23:09.375
And then down.

02:23:09.875 --> 02:23:13.583
And this hand should move straight.

02:23:16.999 --> 02:23:19.959
Attention should be on the left hand.

02:23:22.083 --> 02:23:25.000
Now, try to move the hand properly.

02:23:25.375 --> 02:23:27.041
On top of your head you have to take it,

02:23:27.333 --> 02:23:28.750
take it on top of your head.

02:23:28.959 --> 02:23:33.083
Bend back your head, and give it a twist,

02:23:33.500 --> 02:23:36.125
and give it a twist, big twist,

02:23:36.542 --> 02:23:39.709
and tie it up like a knot.

02:23:40.417 --> 02:23:45.542
Again let's do, to fix it up properly. Again do it, please.

02:23:46.500 --> 02:23:49.041
Second time, let's just do it.

02:23:49.417 --> 02:23:52.959
Now push back your head, and give it a big twist,

02:23:55.250 --> 02:23:57.291
and give it a knot.

02:23:57.667 --> 02:24:01.083
Now, third time same way, but three knots.

02:24:04.250 --> 02:24:05.709
Again.

02:24:06.041 --> 02:24:08.542
Now it's moving fast.

02:24:09.083 --> 02:24:11.417
Put it - now one,

02:24:12.999 --> 02:24:15.083
again give a twist;

02:24:15.458 --> 02:24:17.000
two,

02:24:17.333 --> 02:24:20.208
again a twist; and a three.

02:24:20.542 --> 02:24:23.542
Now see your hands.

02:24:26.999 --> 02:24:29.792
You feel much lighter.

02:24:35.625 --> 02:24:39.417
Feel it on your head also, cool breeze coming out.

02:24:43.625 --> 02:24:46.458
You'll be absolutely relaxed.

02:24:47.041 --> 02:24:49.125
You cannot think now;

02:24:49.542 --> 02:24:51.166
but if you want, you can.

02:24:51.500 --> 02:24:55.250
But don't think about it, you can't think about it.

02:24:59.999 --> 02:25:03.500
Just feel it - all of you have got it.

02:25:10.834 --> 02:25:12.875
Good!

02:25:13.291 --> 02:25:16.583
You'll see, your eyes will be sparkling.

02:25:16.625 --> 02:25:19.458
There will be light in your eye.

02:25:23.375 --> 02:25:25.291
Now, you don't think.

02:25:25.583 --> 02:25:27.542
Otherwise next time when I come, you'll say,

02:25:27.834 --> 02:25:30.125
"Mother, I have lost my vibrations."

02:25:33.458 --> 02:25:36.083
If you think about it you cannot reach there.

02:25:43.000 --> 02:25:45.959
All right. Now if you want to shake hands with Me,

02:25:46.166 --> 02:25:47.667
I will sit here for you for a while.

02:25:47.999 --> 02:25:49.375
You can come round to shake hands.

02:25:49.667 --> 02:25:51.000
But Sahaja yogis, you need not

02:25:52.333 --> 02:25:55.083
- otherwise there's just no end to it!

02:26:14.375 --> 02:26:17.208
Ah, ah. You can come here and see.

02:26:17.542 --> 02:26:21.291
Did you feel the cool breeze? Did you? Now that I can see.

