All right. Just a minute, please, just a minute.

02:26:41.166 --> 02:26:44.667
Hallo, how are you? Felt it? You've enjoyed it?

02:26:51.709 --> 02:26:53.500
Hallo, how are you?

02:26:53.792 --> 02:26:55.999
May God bless you.

